WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:05.690 --> 00:00:07.190
Harm-Marshal
Vanilla Peschutz

3
00:00:08.110 --> 00:00:11.190
A proud lady like myself needs no friends!

4
00:00:12.740 --> 00:00:15.410
All right. I'll tell you a secret.

5
00:00:15.410 --> 00:00:16.700
Your Highness?

6
00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:23.660
I also believed that a proud 
knight like myself needs no friends.

7
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:25.460
But...

8
00:00:26.290 --> 00:00:27.790
The truth is...

9
00:00:27.790 --> 00:00:29.710
I wanted friends.

10
00:00:30.710 --> 00:00:33.340
Me, too.

11
00:00:38.850 --> 00:00:41.310
<i>My very first friend!</i>

12
00:00:41.850 --> 00:00:44.440
<i>I want to hang out with 
her, just the two of us!</i>

13
00:00:45.390 --> 00:00:49.060
<i>But I'm the daughter of the 
noble House of Peschutz.</i>

14
00:00:49.060 --> 00:00:52.570
<i>It'd be totally unacceptable to invite her!</i>

15
00:00:53.070 --> 00:00:55.860
The princess should be the one who asks <i>me</i>!

16
00:00:55.860 --> 00:00:59.690
Nothing says a prisoner can't invite 
her torturer to go have some fun!

17
00:01:01.080 --> 00:01:03.410
No, that's not it.

18
00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.130
It's not the family name that's stopping me.

19
00:01:08.130 --> 00:01:10.340
I just can't work up the courage.

20
00:01:11.130 --> 00:01:14.170
Blaming my upbringing 
for my own cowardice...

21
00:01:14.170 --> 00:01:15.920
Some Peschutz I am!

22
00:01:17.130 --> 00:01:20.640
It's time to show my courage and rise up!

23
00:01:22.140 --> 00:01:26.060
But where could we even go?

24
00:01:32.190 --> 00:01:34.230
<i>Zoom!</i>

25
00:01:35.980 --> 00:01:36.860
<i>Yay!</i>

26
00:01:36.860 --> 00:01:38.160
<i>Wow!</i>

27
00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:39.990
<i>How did you do that?!</i>

28
00:01:40.740 --> 00:01:42.700
<i>Not telling!</i>

29
00:01:41.370 --> 00:01:42.700
What are you watching?

30
00:01:42.700 --> 00:01:44.370
<i>Not fair!</i>

31
00:01:42.700 --> 00:01:47.410
Oh, a video of Jimochi and me going 
ice skating after ditching lessons.

32
00:01:47.410 --> 00:01:49.380
That damn geezer, I swear...

33
00:01:48.290 --> 00:01:50.580
<i>You're so awesome, Jimochi!</i>

34
00:01:49.630 --> 00:01:53.170
Man, I'd love to go skating again.

35
00:01:53.170 --> 00:01:55.090
Ice skating sounds great!

36
00:01:55.090 --> 00:01:56.590
You can skate, Ex?

37
00:01:57.090 --> 00:02:00.140
My specialty is the quadruple Salchow!

38
00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:02.100
Huh...

39
00:02:02.600 --> 00:02:04.060
Ah! You don't believe me!

40
00:02:04.430 --> 00:02:07.060
<i>Ice skating! That's it!</i>

41
00:02:08.980 --> 00:02:10.730
<i>The House of Peschutz.</i>

42
00:02:10.730 --> 00:02:13.770
<i>Descended from Melaarc Peschutz,</i>

43
00:02:13.770 --> 00:02:16.530
<i>the clandestine right-hand 
man of the first Hell-Lord,</i>

44
00:02:16.530 --> 00:02:18.650
<i>they are a noble clan of vampires.</i>

45
00:02:18.950 --> 00:02:23.530
<i>They will use any means necessary to 
achieve their ends, stopping at nothing.</i>

46
00:02:23.530 --> 00:02:29.040
<i>Rumors say they are the most ruthlessly 
brutal among the Hellhorde.</i>

47
00:02:26.040 --> 00:02:29.040
Current Head
Aliotto Peschutz

48
00:02:30.950 --> 00:02:33.210
Book it out!

49
00:02:33.420 --> 00:02:35.670
Aliotto's Wife
Extrac Peschutz

50
00:02:33.960 --> 00:02:35.670
What's the matter, dear?

51
00:02:35.670 --> 00:02:36.630
Honey!

52
00:02:36.630 --> 00:02:40.180
We need to book out all of Peschutz 
Ice Skating Rink for tomorrow!

53
00:02:40.180 --> 00:02:41.130
Book it out?

54
00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:43.600
That's impossible on such short notice.

55
00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:45.760
We have group reservations—

56
00:02:44.930 --> 00:02:47.560
Listen to what Vanilla-chan just told me!

57
00:02:48.770 --> 00:02:49.980
Papa.

58
00:02:49.980 --> 00:02:53.280
Can I get a ticket for the ice rink?

59
00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:57.570
Vanilla-chan, you know you can ask the 
front desk and get in without a ticket.

60
00:02:57.570 --> 00:03:00.740
Ah, um, well...

61
00:03:01.780 --> 00:03:04.530
I wanted to go with a friend.

62
00:03:04.530 --> 00:03:06.290
A friend?!

63
00:03:06.290 --> 00:03:09.530
Fr-Frie... Friend... Fr...

64
00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:07.370
Yeah.

65
00:03:08.040 --> 00:03:09.540
The other day, for the first time...

66
00:03:10.210 --> 00:03:12.120
I made a friend.

67
00:03:12.420 --> 00:03:16.050
Fr-Friend...

68
00:03:12.420 --> 00:03:16.250
I made a friend...

69
00:03:18.630 --> 00:03:20.550
Let's book it out!

70
00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:24.220
So that Vanilla-chan can spend a 
day having fun with her friend!

71
00:03:24.220 --> 00:03:29.180
The cancellation fees for the reservations 
are a small price to pay!

72
00:03:29.810 --> 00:03:33.940
<i>They will use any means necessary to 
achieve their ends, stopping at nothing.</i>

73
00:03:33.940 --> 00:03:37.190
<i>That is the way of the 
noble House of Peschutz.</i>

74
00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:42.660
Hmm...

75
00:03:42.660 --> 00:03:44.370
I don't think this is it.

76
00:03:44.740 --> 00:03:46.120
I know!

77
00:03:47.910 --> 00:03:51.080
The outfit I saved to wear 
on a special occasion.

78
00:03:55.210 --> 00:03:56.540
There we go!

79
00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:59.880
Perfect for my first time 
hanging out with a friend!

80
00:04:01.500 --> 00:04:03.380
Peschutz Ice Skating Rink

81
00:04:03.380 --> 00:04:06.260
Notice for Visitors
We are booked today for
a private event.
We apologize to all
of our customers.
Thank you for your
understanding.

82
00:04:08.180 --> 00:04:10.520
Wow! This place is huge!

83
00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:12.360
Not a scratch on the ice!

84
00:04:13.440 --> 00:04:15.060
What do you think, Princess?

85
00:04:15.060 --> 00:04:16.270
The noble House of Peschutz

86
00:04:16.270 --> 00:04:20.610
is focused more on the sports industry 
than vampire services nowadays.

87
00:04:20.610 --> 00:04:22.430
Vampirism is a business now?

88
00:04:22.740 --> 00:04:25.700
This ice rink is operated 
by the Peschutz family!

89
00:04:25.700 --> 00:04:28.900
Thanks to my noble powers, 
it's booked out for the day!

90
00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:31.080
B-Booked out?!

91
00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:31.950
Well?

92
00:04:31.950 --> 00:04:32.830
Do you feel humbled?

93
00:04:32.830 --> 00:04:34.880
That's amazing, Vanilla-chan!

94
00:04:36.080 --> 00:04:37.130
Yeah...

95
00:04:38.040 --> 00:04:41.390
Well, the amazing ones are 
actually Mama and Papa.

96
00:04:41.390 --> 00:04:44.050
O-Okay, should we skate toge—

97
00:04:44.050 --> 00:04:45.050
I get it.

98
00:04:45.050 --> 00:04:47.430
So today's torture is ice skating!

99
00:04:47.430 --> 00:04:48.010
Huh?

100
00:04:48.010 --> 00:04:51.890
You prepared this torture knowing 
that I wanted to go skating!

101
00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:55.020
Pretty good, Vanilla-chan!

102
00:04:55.020 --> 00:04:57.270
I-I sure am!

103
00:04:57.650 --> 00:05:02.360
But you forget that I'm the Princess and 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion!

104
00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:04.780
I will not lose to ice skating!

105
00:05:05.570 --> 00:05:06.990
<i>Dang it!</i>

106
00:05:06.990 --> 00:05:09.700
<i>Now it's being treated like torture!</i>

107
00:05:10.030 --> 00:05:10.990
Go on!

108
00:05:10.990 --> 00:05:13.000
Show me your skating form!

109
00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:15.370
If I end up tempted and step 
into the rink, I lose!

110
00:05:15.370 --> 00:05:17.880
Well, I'll definitely resist, though!

111
00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:20.950
If only you had more to show 
for that big talk of yours...

112
00:05:20.950 --> 00:05:23.210
Go on now, Vanilla-chan!

113
00:05:23.210 --> 00:05:25.670
Ah, yeah...

114
00:05:26.260 --> 00:05:28.340
Okay, Princess.

115
00:05:29.140 --> 00:05:31.560
Time for your torture...

116
00:05:39.940 --> 00:05:41.900
<i>Ah, whoops.</i>

117
00:05:41.900 --> 00:05:44.530
<i>I've never ice skated before.</i>

118
00:05:44.530 --> 00:05:48.570
Whoa, whoa, whoa...

119
00:05:48.990 --> 00:05:51.370
<i>I was too busy thinking about 
hanging out with the princess!</i>

120
00:05:51.370 --> 00:05:54.070
<i>I completely forgot that I can't skate!</i>

121
00:05:54.070 --> 00:05:58.330
<i>And my clumsy way of inviting her 
made her think this is torture...</i>

122
00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:01.340
<i>Ah, jeez!</i>

123
00:06:04.710 --> 00:06:06.670
<i>If I knew this would happen...</i>

124
00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:11.550
<i>I wouldn't have worked up my courage...</i>

125
00:06:23.610 --> 00:06:25.150
I made it!

126
00:06:25.150 --> 00:06:26.890
Princess?

127
00:06:27.280 --> 00:06:29.700
Um, by entering the rink...

128
00:06:29.700 --> 00:06:32.140
Yeah, I admit defeat.

129
00:06:32.140 --> 00:06:35.960
But more importantly, I'm 
glad you didn't fall over.

130
00:06:38.950 --> 00:06:41.960
Prinshess!

131
00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:41.960
Huh?

132
00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:43.420
What's wrong, Vanilla-chan?

133
00:06:43.420 --> 00:06:44.460
Calm down!

134
00:06:44.460 --> 00:06:46.050
I'll tell you a secret!

135
00:06:46.050 --> 00:06:49.840
You don't need to do that!

136
00:06:48.510 --> 00:06:50.380
Huh? Why not?

137
00:06:50.380 --> 00:06:52.340
B-Because...

138
00:06:52.340 --> 00:06:54.640
t-today wasn't supposed to be...

139
00:06:54.640 --> 00:07:01.150
Wait, this wasn't torture, and you 
just wanted to go skating with me?

140
00:07:01.650 --> 00:07:03.560
N-No way!

141
00:07:03.560 --> 00:07:06.600
It's not like I'd ever... ever...

142
00:07:10.280 --> 00:07:12.860
It's fine, I'll share a secret.

143
00:07:14.460 --> 00:07:16.370
Today's secret is...

144
00:07:16.790 --> 00:07:19.710
the imperial technique to 
get better at skating!

145
00:07:29.420 --> 00:07:30.760
Yeah, that's it.

146
00:07:31.130 --> 00:07:34.750
Try not to kick backwards, but 
use the side of your foot.

147
00:07:35.010 --> 00:07:37.350
Well? Think you got it?

148
00:07:37.350 --> 00:07:38.100
Yeah.

149
00:07:38.810 --> 00:07:39.850
This is fun!

150
00:07:40.140 --> 00:07:41.270
Glad to hear it!

151
00:07:43.980 --> 00:07:47.070
Vanilla-chan, that outfit 
looks great on you.

152
00:07:47.070 --> 00:07:48.150
So cute!

153
00:07:48.150 --> 00:07:50.030
Prinshess!

154
00:07:50.150 --> 00:07:52.610
The two of them
had fun

155
00:07:52.610 --> 00:07:56.620
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

156
00:07:52.860 --> 00:07:54.450
Up you go!

157
00:07:54.450 --> 00:07:55.780
Up I go?!

158
00:07:58.160 --> 00:08:01.370
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

159
00:08:05.580 --> 00:08:06.960
Is something the matter?

160
00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:09.000
You seem quite listless.

161
00:08:09.380 --> 00:08:10.920
Are you feeling unwell?

162
00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:11.880
What?!

163
00:08:11.880 --> 00:08:15.300
H-Hmph! In your dreams!

164
00:08:15.300 --> 00:08:18.140
I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion!

165
00:08:18.470 --> 00:08:20.810
I'm in tip-top shape at all times!

166
00:08:20.810 --> 00:08:22.980
There's no way that I'd be feeling sick!

167
00:08:25.020 --> 00:08:29.860
Did you think the slightest change 
to your condition would escape me?

168
00:08:32.400 --> 00:08:34.320
37.2 degrees.

169
00:08:34.610 --> 00:08:35.490
See?

170
00:08:35.490 --> 00:08:37.320
Told you it wasn't a big deal!

171
00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:39.330
What are you talking about?

172
00:08:39.330 --> 00:08:44.330
Considering your normal body temperature, 
this is plenty worrisome.

173
00:08:44.670 --> 00:08:47.670
I'm sure you must be feeling quite ill.

174
00:08:47.670 --> 00:08:52.840
Ex, whose power is intertwined with you, 
is all tuckered out and silent.

175
00:08:53.550 --> 00:08:58.180
I'll call off today's torture, 
so please get some rest.

176
00:08:59.510 --> 00:09:04.390
I'm an Imperial Commander, 
and yet you take pity on me?

177
00:09:04.770 --> 00:09:06.900
How utterly insulting!

178
00:09:09.650 --> 00:09:12.640
It's so soft and warm!

179
00:09:14.030 --> 00:09:19.160
During marches, I would have 
to camp outside a lot.

180
00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:23.870
My body's capable of sleeping comfortably 
even in rocky areas and other hard places...

181
00:09:23.870 --> 00:09:27.370
But a futon really does feel so nice!

182
00:09:27.370 --> 00:09:31.300
Would you prefer congee or udon for lunch?

183
00:09:31.300 --> 00:09:32.880
I get to pick?!

184
00:09:32.880 --> 00:09:34.760
Um, in that case...

185
00:09:35.050 --> 00:09:36.260
Udon!

186
00:09:45.020 --> 00:09:46.730
It's good!

187
00:09:48.980 --> 00:09:50.150
Pudding!

188
00:09:50.150 --> 00:09:51.020
I can have it?

189
00:09:51.520 --> 00:09:53.610
It's a special treat for today.

190
00:09:55.030 --> 00:09:56.650
Hooray!

191
00:10:01.410 --> 00:10:04.160
Demon World
Shocking

192
00:10:01.410 --> 00:10:04.160
5th Appearance
After 10 Years

193
00:10:01.410 --> 00:10:04.160
Actor: Kyo Yoshizawa

194
00:10:01.780 --> 00:10:03.040
<i>How've you been?</i>

195
00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:04.160
<i>Did you cut your hair?</i>

196
00:10:04.160 --> 00:10:07.410
Bamboo! Bamboo poles!

197
00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:08.900
<i>Boy, we received more 
flowers than ever today!</i>

198
00:10:09.420 --> 00:10:13.000
<i>Huh? There's even some from Hige and Nazca!</i>

199
00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:15.630
<i>Ah, you starred in that drama with them!</i>

200
00:10:16.260 --> 00:10:17.970
That should do it.

201
00:10:17.970 --> 00:10:20.800
Princess, are you thirsty?

202
00:10:26.770 --> 00:10:28.730
The princess
got some sleep

203
00:10:29.400 --> 00:10:30.480
What?

204
00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:32.230
The princess caught a cold?

205
00:10:32.520 --> 00:10:33.610
Yes.

206
00:10:33.610 --> 00:10:35.900
Torture is currently nursing 
her back to health.

207
00:10:35.900 --> 00:10:37.570
Geh-heh-heh.

208
00:10:37.570 --> 00:10:39.360
Hope she feels better.

209
00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:44.280
It seems that humans have difficulty with 
the Demon World's wild temperature swings.

210
00:10:44.280 --> 00:10:46.080
Geh-heh-heh.

211
00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:50.360
Humans are such fragile 
and delicate creatures.

212
00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:51.880
So be it!

213
00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:58.340
If that's the case, then let her keep 
the futon even after she recovers!

214
00:11:01.140 --> 00:11:03.970
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

215
00:11:09.770 --> 00:11:11.810
The princess made
a full recovery

216
00:11:12.860 --> 00:11:16.230
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

217
00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:18.690
What's wrong, Torture?

218
00:11:18.690 --> 00:11:19.950
You don't seem very chipper.

219
00:11:19.950 --> 00:11:22.200
No, that's not true at all...

220
00:11:23.410 --> 00:11:25.950
Did you think the slightest 
change to your condition...

221
00:11:26.410 --> 00:11:28.200
would escape me?!

222
00:11:29.330 --> 00:11:31.120
Well done, Princess.

223
00:11:31.120 --> 00:11:33.080
It seems I can't keep a secret from you.

224
00:11:33.460 --> 00:11:34.710
What happened?

225
00:11:35.170 --> 00:11:37.840
This is classified information, actually...

226
00:11:37.840 --> 00:11:40.880
but there are going to be 
personnel transfers tomorrow.

227
00:11:40.880 --> 00:11:43.340
The Hellhorde's got personnel 
shakeups, too, huh?

228
00:11:43.680 --> 00:11:48.390
By personnel transfers, you mean 
like changing departments?

229
00:11:48.390 --> 00:11:49.560
Yes.

230
00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:53.150
In other words, our torture 
sessions together...

231
00:11:53.150 --> 00:11:55.860
might end after today.

232
00:11:55.860 --> 00:11:56.650
What?!

233
00:11:57.070 --> 00:12:01.360
As a high-ranking grand inquisitor, 
shouldn't you be safe?!

234
00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:05.570
Torturers are a specialist position, 
so transfers are very rare.

235
00:12:05.570 --> 00:12:07.280
But I can't say for certain.

236
00:12:07.530 --> 00:12:10.330
There's also the possibility of being moved 
from the trenches to a board position.

237
00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:13.040
And not just me, of course.

238
00:12:13.620 --> 00:12:16.710
Someone else could end up 
being transferred as well.

239
00:12:16.710 --> 00:12:17.920
No way...

240
00:12:17.920 --> 00:12:19.550
And tomorrow's the announcement...

241
00:12:20.590 --> 00:12:22.800
Will you be notified before then?

242
00:12:22.800 --> 00:12:23.930
No.

243
00:12:23.930 --> 00:12:27.430
On the morning of, it will 
be posted by the entrance.

244
00:12:24.760 --> 00:12:26.350
Hellhorde Personnel

245
00:12:26.350 --> 00:12:28.720
Hellhorde Personnel

246
00:12:27.430 --> 00:12:28.720
What is this, a classroom shuffle?

247
00:12:29.060 --> 00:12:34.480
Of course, I could continue to 
be entrusted with you as well.

248
00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:36.860
Torture...

249
00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:41.570
Even if they split us up, we should 
still grab lunch together...

250
00:12:41.570 --> 00:12:42.990
What is this, a classroom shuffle?

251
00:12:42.990 --> 00:12:44.860
Oh, my apologies.

252
00:12:44.860 --> 00:12:47.780
I didn't mean to make things so somber.

253
00:12:47.780 --> 00:12:52.500
This might be our last time, so we 
wouldn't want to end on such a sad note!

254
00:12:52.500 --> 00:12:53.960
I will not give in!

255
00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:57.250
When you said that this 
might be our last time,

256
00:12:57.250 --> 00:13:00.460
I made up my mind to never give in today!

257
00:13:00.920 --> 00:13:05.510
Torture! You'll never make 
me surrender as you are!

258
00:13:06.300 --> 00:13:09.760
Not while you're alone, that is!

259
00:13:12.810 --> 00:13:13.600
What?

260
00:13:16.190 --> 00:13:17.810
Is that right?

261
00:13:17.810 --> 00:13:20.700
Then I suppose I have no 
choice but to call for help.

262
00:13:22.690 --> 00:13:24.400
The final torture...

263
00:13:24.900 --> 00:13:26.820
Everyone, assemble!

264
00:13:28.910 --> 00:13:30.370
Here we go, Prinshess!

265
00:13:30.370 --> 00:13:31.540
Here we come!

266
00:13:31.540 --> 00:13:33.410
Get ready, Princess-chan!

267
00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:37.370
Prepare yourself, Princess!

268
00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:39.040
Let's go!

269
00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:43.420
I am the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion!

270
00:13:43.420 --> 00:13:47.090
I will never submit to such 
feeble torture as this!

271
00:13:54.180 --> 00:13:55.310
Where'd you end up?

272
00:13:55.310 --> 00:13:57.140
It says I'm in the Fourth Army!

273
00:13:56.690 --> 00:14:00.190
The next day

274
00:13:57.140 --> 00:13:59.100
Whoa, look who's moving up.

275
00:13:59.100 --> 00:14:00.190
Wowie.

276
00:14:00.190 --> 00:14:02.690
We'll need to celebrate.

277
00:14:02.690 --> 00:14:04.690
Hellhorde Personnel

278
00:14:10.030 --> 00:14:11.280
Torture!

279
00:14:12.330 --> 00:14:13.580
Princess?!

280
00:14:14.790 --> 00:14:16.160
What are you doing out—

281
00:14:18.210 --> 00:14:21.210
Awesome! We're all together again!

282
00:14:22.040 --> 00:14:25.210
G-Grand Inquisitor.

283
00:14:25.210 --> 00:14:29.050
It's an honor to report to you again.

284
00:14:29.050 --> 00:14:31.140
We'll torture 'em real good!

285
00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:39.230
Princess, I look forward to 
spending more time together.

286
00:14:39.230 --> 00:14:40.440
Yeah!

287
00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:42.980
Just know that I won't surrender!

288
00:14:56.700 --> 00:14:58.910
The princess
confessed

289
00:16:43.940 --> 00:16:45.480
Where am I?

290
00:16:45.480 --> 00:16:47.440
So you've come to.

291
00:16:52.530 --> 00:16:55.740
We've been reincarnated in another world.

292
00:16:57.160 --> 00:16:57.990
What?

293
00:16:59.660 --> 00:17:00.910
What's the meaning of this?

294
00:17:01.410 --> 00:17:02.790
The Hell-Lord's body double!

295
00:17:02.790 --> 00:17:04.040
Please explain this!

296
00:17:03.790 --> 00:17:07.290
The princess and Ex think the Hell-Lord is his own body double

297
00:17:04.040 --> 00:17:07.290
Just as we'd all gathered 
for a game of basketball...

298
00:17:10.920 --> 00:17:14.170
Do you remember the lightning strike 
during that sudden thunderstorm?

299
00:17:14.760 --> 00:17:18.180
It looks like that caused our 
reincarnation in this parallel world.

300
00:17:19.050 --> 00:17:22.680
We're still alive, so maybe it's 
teleportation to a parallel world?

301
00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:25.480
Either way, you see it all the time in anime.

302
00:17:25.480 --> 00:17:26.850
I don't watch anime.

303
00:17:26.850 --> 00:17:27.900
O-Oh.

304
00:17:28.650 --> 00:17:31.150
So we're in a different world than our own?

305
00:17:31.150 --> 00:17:33.030
How do we get back?

306
00:17:33.570 --> 00:17:38.280
The way it usually works is you can 
go back once you save the world.

307
00:17:38.280 --> 00:17:41.790
I woke up around two hours 
earlier than you did.

308
00:17:41.790 --> 00:17:44.040
I've been exploring our surroundings here.

309
00:17:45.540 --> 00:17:50.000
<i>It looks like this world is under the 
reign of one known as the Black Monarch,</i>

310
00:17:50.000 --> 00:17:52.630
<i>who causes the populace great suffering.</i>

311
00:17:52.630 --> 00:17:53.840
<i>The Black Monarch?!</i>

312
00:17:53.840 --> 00:17:56.380
<i>To reach the Black Monarch's palace,</i>

313
00:17:56.380 --> 00:18:01.640
<i>one must vanquish the Four Horsemen of 
Darkness, who reside in the Black Tower.</i>

314
00:18:00.390 --> 00:18:02.100
The Black Tower

315
00:18:02.100 --> 00:18:07.270
<i>As for the Four Horsemen, I defeated them 
all while I happened to be out investigating.</i>

316
00:18:03.770 --> 00:18:09.440
The Four Horsemen of Darkness

317
00:18:07.850 --> 00:18:09.440
<i>You defeated them?!</i>

318
00:18:09.440 --> 00:18:12.320
<i>As I wandered the Dark Wastelands...</i>

319
00:18:09.810 --> 00:18:12.320
The Dark Wastelands

320
00:18:15.440 --> 00:18:19.070
Never thought someone would show 
up and beat the Four Horsemen.

321
00:18:19.570 --> 00:18:22.620
But don't get cocky just yet.

322
00:18:22.620 --> 00:18:23.910
Did you know?

323
00:18:23.910 --> 00:18:28.620
The Four Horsemen of Darkness have 
a Dark Power Level of 15 at best!

324
00:18:28.620 --> 00:18:30.250
<i>Explain this Dark Power Level thing first!</i>

325
00:18:31.090 --> 00:18:33.000
I am Garyuo!

326
00:18:31.330 --> 00:18:33.000
Garyuo

327
00:18:33.460 --> 00:18:37.000
My Dark Power Level is 100!

328
00:18:34.460 --> 00:18:37.010
Dark Power Level:

329
00:18:41.510 --> 00:18:43.560
<i>After defeating Garyuo,</i>

330
00:18:43.560 --> 00:18:47.180
<i>the Gate of Darkness leading 
to the Black Palace appeared.</i>

331
00:18:47.180 --> 00:18:49.730
<i>Garyuo got done in with his introduction!</i>

332
00:18:47.230 --> 00:18:49.730
Gate of Darkness

333
00:18:51.150 --> 00:18:54.980
<i>I passed through the Gate of 
Darkness to the Black Palace.</i>

334
00:18:53.230 --> 00:18:59.320
The Black Palace

335
00:18:54.980 --> 00:18:59.320
<i>Awaiting me there were the 
Black Monarch's loyal minions:</i>

336
00:18:59.320 --> 00:19:00.610
<i>The Nine Darknesses.</i>

337
00:18:59.360 --> 00:19:08.080
Minions of the Black Monarch: The Nine Darknesses

338
00:19:00.610 --> 00:19:04.830
<i>All mighty warriors, with Dark 
Power Levels exceeding 5,000.</i>

339
00:19:04.830 --> 00:19:08.080
<i>The irreversible power 
inflation's already begun!</i>

340
00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:11.290
Well, I managed to take them 
down after this and that,

341
00:19:11.290 --> 00:19:15.130
and thus, I reached the throne 
room of the Black Monarch.

342
00:19:15.130 --> 00:19:17.590
"This and that" are all the 
Nine Darknesses get, huh?

343
00:19:23.930 --> 00:19:28.220
Steamed Buns of Darkness

344
00:19:24.050 --> 00:19:27.100
So you've made it this far.

345
00:19:26.600 --> 00:19:29.060
The Black Monarch

346
00:19:27.100 --> 00:19:29.060
Unfortunately for you,

347
00:19:29.060 --> 00:19:31.310
my Dark Power Level is...

348
00:19:31.310 --> 00:19:33.020
980,000.

349
00:19:33.020 --> 00:19:37.230
Dark Power Level:

350
00:19:33.770 --> 00:19:37.230
<i>Now I feel sorry for Garyuo, showing 
off with a Dark Power Level of 100.</i>

351
00:19:37.230 --> 00:19:41.200
What's more, without the 
heavenly dragons' treasure,

352
00:19:41.200 --> 00:19:44.870
the Sacred Skymitar, my 
body cannot be pierced.

353
00:19:44.870 --> 00:19:47.960
<i>Why is he giving you hints 
on how to beat him?</i>

354
00:19:47.960 --> 00:19:52.210
<i>And so, I went into battle 
against the Black Monarch!</i>

355
00:19:54.750 --> 00:19:56.420
<i>What's with the song?!</i>

356
00:20:03.760 --> 00:20:09.770
<i>No manner of slashing spell was able to 
make even a scratch on the Black Monarch.</i>

357
00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:12.810
Is that all you've got?!

358
00:20:12.810 --> 00:20:15.980
My Soul of Darkness, imbued with 
the power of the Black Moon,

359
00:20:15.980 --> 00:20:19.280
has been led by the Dark Light and 
burns darkly with the Black Flames,

360
00:20:19.280 --> 00:20:21.070
mastering the Way of the Dark!

361
00:20:21.070 --> 00:20:23.360
The Road of Darkness!

362
00:20:23.360 --> 00:20:24.780
<i>Dirt cheap prices on darkness!</i>

363
00:20:26.580 --> 00:20:28.410
Now it's time I make my move.

364
00:20:28.410 --> 00:20:33.210
I'll finish you off and engulf the world 
in darkness with my Dark Power Level.

365
00:20:35.580 --> 00:20:37.170
Black Sword!

366
00:20:37.500 --> 00:20:41.220
Can you withstand my Special Dark Attack?!

367
00:20:47.350 --> 00:20:48.140
Eh?

368
00:20:51.140 --> 00:20:54.310
<i>My slashing spells had no effect on him.</i>

369
00:20:56.230 --> 00:20:59.150
<i>So I punched the living 
daylights out of him.</i>

370
00:21:09.140 --> 00:21:10.340
<i>Man, this is long...</i>

371
00:21:25.350 --> 00:21:30.810
And so, I vanquished the Black 
Monarch, and returned here.

372
00:21:30.810 --> 00:21:33.950
So you saved the world in 
two hours, give or take?

373
00:21:33.950 --> 00:21:35.440
What?

374
00:21:35.440 --> 00:21:37.390
The body double saved the world?

375
00:21:37.760 --> 00:21:40.840
I normally try and act 
with the utmost caution,

376
00:21:40.840 --> 00:21:44.320
but I couldn't forgive the Black Monarch 
after learning of his evil deeds.

377
00:21:44.900 --> 00:21:49.410
Also, I've always dreamed of being 
reincarnated in another world...

378
00:21:49.410 --> 00:21:51.420
So I got a little excited!

379
00:21:51.420 --> 00:21:53.460
So I got a little excited!

380
00:21:53.460 --> 00:21:56.700
So I got a little excited!

381
00:21:57.570 --> 00:21:59.860
Such strength for only a body double...

382
00:21:59.860 --> 00:22:02.890
Yeah, the Imperial Army's in danger.

383
00:22:02.890 --> 00:22:06.190
The Imperial Army commands a 
much larger force than we do.

384
00:22:06.190 --> 00:22:07.180
Besides...

385
00:22:07.680 --> 00:22:12.420
What good can come from crushing your 
opponent with overwhelming force?

386
00:22:18.980 --> 00:22:20.800
The Black Clouds have vanished!

387
00:22:20.800 --> 00:22:22.830
Could it be that the Black Monarch...

388
00:22:23.590 --> 00:22:25.770
Th-That reminds me, earlier...

389
00:22:25.770 --> 00:22:29.940
A strange man came around asking 
about the Black Monarch.

390
00:22:30.800 --> 00:22:32.660
It's the great hero...

391
00:22:33.280 --> 00:22:34.690
That can't be!

392
00:22:34.690 --> 00:22:39.300
"When the world falls to darkness, a hero 
bearing a sacred sword will appear."

393
00:22:39.300 --> 00:22:40.780
The one from that legend?!

394
00:22:40.780 --> 00:22:44.710
Wait, the legend says that a new 
calamity appears with the hero, too!

395
00:22:44.710 --> 00:22:46.970
The King of the Demon World!

396
00:22:46.970 --> 00:22:51.810
He must have defeated the King 
of the Demon World as well.

397
00:22:52.260 --> 00:22:56.550
Praise be to the hero!

398
00:23:09.280 --> 00:23:10.550
Princess-chan!

399
00:23:10.550 --> 00:23:13.480
Just where have you two been?

400
00:23:14.240 --> 00:23:16.730
Man, looks like we ended 
up in another world.

401
00:23:17.290 --> 00:23:18.740
I'm relieved to see you safe.

402
00:23:19.080 --> 00:23:22.060
I was real worried after 
you left all of a sudden!

403
00:23:22.060 --> 00:23:23.550
Geh-heh-heh.

404
00:23:23.550 --> 00:23:25.430
I'm sorry about that.

405
00:23:26.170 --> 00:23:28.890
Well then, let's take it from the top...

406
00:23:31.030 --> 00:23:34.230
And have ourselves a nice 
game of basketball!

407
00:23:33.910 --> 00:23:38.910
